{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"↩\n            ↪\n          \n          \n            B\n            I\n            S\n            U\n            H\n            x²\n            x₂\n          \n          \n            H ▾\n            ≡\n            1.\n            ☑\n          \n          \n            ⟨/⟩\n            { } ▾\n            🔗\n            🖼\n            ▦\n          \n          \n          Ready\n        \n        \n        \n          Insert\n          \n            Admonition ▾\n            Tabs\n            Math ▾\n            Mermaid\n            Keys\n            HR\n            Footnote\n            😊\n          \n          \n          ↓ .md\n        \n      \n    \n    \n      B — Two Rows, Clear Hierarchy\n      Row 1 = formatting & structure (what you use constantly). Row 2 = block inserts (what you use occasionally) with an \"Insert\" label. Keeps everything visible but with clear visual priority. Similar to current but much more polished.","choice":"two-rows","id":null,"timestamp":1774362164358}
