{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"⠿\n          An idle block — always has a faint background card and border. You can always see where one block ends and another begins.\n        \n        \n        \n          ⠿\n          ⚙\n          Hovered. Background slightly brightens, subtle shadow lifts. Blocks feel like physical cards you can grab and rearrange.\n        \n        \n        \n          ⠿\n          ⚙\n          The active block. Bold purple accent border, card elevates slightly. Clear visual feedback — you know exactly where you are.\n        \n        \n        \n          \n            def hello():\n                print(\"world\")\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      B — Defined & Tactile\n      Blocks always have a faint card background. You always see boundaries. Hover lifts the card with a shadow. Active gets a bold accent. Feels like dragging tangible cards. More structured, less minimal.","choice":"defined-tactile","id":null,"timestamp":1774362277591}
{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"⠿\n          An idle paragraph block. The drag handle is barely visible. No border, no background change. Content speaks.\n        \n        \n        \n          ⠿\n          ⚙\n          A hovered block. Very subtle border appears, drag handle fades in, gear icon fades in on the right.\n          paragraph\n        \n        \n        \n          ⠿\n          ⚙\n          The active block. Soft purple glow border, slight background tint. Cursor is blinking here.\n        \n        \n        \n          \n            def hello():\n                print(\"world\")\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      A — Subtle & Airy\n      Generous spacing between blocks. Barely-visible chrome when idle. Hover shows a whisper-thin border and fades in handles. Active gets a soft glow. Block type label appears on hover. Feels like writing on a clean page.","choice":"subtle-airy","id":null,"timestamp":1774362278707}
